#. <section class="sutta" id="mn143"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn143:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 143"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 143"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn143:0.2"
msgid "Anāthapiṇḍikovādasutta"
msgstr "Advice to Anāthapiṇḍika"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.258"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn143:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito "
"bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the householder Anāthapiṇḍika was sick, suffering, gravely "
"ill."

msgctxt "mn143:2.2"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then he addressed a man:"

#. VAR: pāde sirasā vandāhi → vandāhi evañca vadehi (s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: bhagavato pāde sirasā vandāhi → vandāhi evañca vadehi (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "mn143:2.3"
msgid ""
"“ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā mama "
"vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vandāhi:"
msgstr ""
"“Please, mister, go to the Buddha, and in my name bow with your head to his "
"feet. Say to him:"

msgctxt "mn143:2.4"
msgid "‘anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr "‘Sir, the householder Anāthapiṇḍika is sick, suffering, gravely ill."

msgctxt "mn143:2.5"
msgid "So bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatī’ti."
msgstr "He bows with his head to your feet.’"

msgctxt "mn143:2.6"
msgid ""
"Yena cāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena āyasmato "
"sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandāhi:"
msgstr ""
"Then go to Venerable Sāriputta, and in my name bow with your head to his "
"feet. Say to him:"

msgctxt "mn143:2.7"
msgid "‘anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr "‘Sir, the householder Anāthapiṇḍika is sick, suffering, gravely ill."

msgctxt "mn143:2.8"
msgid "So āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandatī’ti."
msgstr "He bows with his head to your feet.’"

msgctxt "mn143:2.9"
msgid "Evañca vadehi:"
msgstr "And then say:"

msgctxt "mn143:2.10"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa "
"nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti."
msgstr "‘Sir, please visit him at his home out of compassion.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:2.11"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho so puriso anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa paṭissutvā yena "
"bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ "
"nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” that man replied. He did as Anāthapiṇḍika asked."

msgctxt "mn143:2.12"
msgid "“anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.13"
msgid "So bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.14"
msgid ""
"Yena cāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso āyasmantaṃ "
"sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.15"
msgid "“anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.16"
msgid "So āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.17"
msgid "evañca vadeti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.18"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa "
"nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:2.19"
msgid "Adhivāsesi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr "Sāriputta consented in silence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.259"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya āyasmatā ānandena "
"pacchāsamaṇena yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. Nisajja kho āyasmā sāriputto "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Sāriputta robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and "
"robe, went with Venerable Ānanda as his second monk to Anāthapiṇḍika’s home. "
"He sat down on the seat spread out, and said to Anāthapiṇḍika:"

msgctxt "mn143:3.2"
msgid ""
"“kacci te, gahapati, khamanīyaṃ, kacci yāpanīyaṃ? Kacci te dukkhā vedanā "
"paṭikkamanti, no abhikkamanti; paṭikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no abhikkamo”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Householder, I hope you’re keeping well; I hope you’re alright. And I hope "
"the pain is fading, not growing, that its fading is evident, not its "
"growing.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Na me, bhante sāriputta, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā "
"abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo."
msgstr ""
"“I’m not keeping well, Master Sāriputta, I’m not alright. The pain is "
"terrible and growing, not fading, its growing, not its fading, is evident."

#. VAR: muddhani → muddhānaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
#. VAR: abhimattheyya → abhimantheyya (bj)
#. VAR: ūhananti → ohananti (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn143:4.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante sāriputta, balavā puriso tiṇhena sikharena muddhani "
"abhimattheyya; evameva kho me, bhante sāriputta, adhimattā vātā muddhani "
"ūhananti."
msgstr ""
"The winds piercing my head are so severe, it feels like a strong man "
"drilling into my head with a sharp point."

msgctxt "mn143:4.3"
msgid ""
"Na me, bhante sāriputta, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā "
"abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sāriputta, adhimattā sīse sīsavedanā → adhimattā vātā sīsaṃ parikantanti (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn143:4.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante sāriputta, balavā puriso daḷhena varattakhaṇḍena sīse "
"sīsaveṭhaṃ dadeyya; evameva kho me, bhante sāriputta, adhimattā sīse "
"sīsavedanā."
msgstr ""
"The pain in my head is so severe, it feels like a strong man tightening a "
"tough leather strap around my head."

msgctxt "mn143:4.5"
msgid ""
"Na me, bhante sāriputta, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā "
"abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:4.6"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante sāriputta, dakkho goghātako vā goghātakantevāsī vā "
"tiṇhena govikantanena kucchiṃ parikanteyya; evameva kho me, bhante "
"sāriputta, adhimattā vātā kucchiṃ parikantanti."
msgstr ""
"The winds piercing my belly are so severe, it feels like an expert butcher "
"or their apprentice is slicing my belly open with a meat cleaver."

msgctxt "mn143:4.7"
msgid ""
"Na me, bhante sāriputta, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā "
"abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:4.8"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante sāriputta, dve balavanto purisā dubbalataraṃ purisaṃ "
"nānābāhāsu gahetvā aṅgārakāsuyā santāpeyyuṃ, samparitāpeyyuṃ; evameva kho "
"me, bhante sāriputta, adhimatto kāyasmiṃ ḍāho."
msgstr ""
"The burning in my body is so severe, it feels like two strong men grabbing a "
"weaker man by the arms to burn and scorch him on a pit of glowing coals. "
"That’s how severe the burning is in my body."

msgctxt "mn143:4.9"
msgid ""
"Na me, bhante sāriputta, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā "
"abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo”ti."
msgstr ""
"I’m not keeping well, Master Sāriputta, I’m not alright. The pain is "
"terrible and growing, not fading, its growing, not its fading, is evident.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:5.1"
msgid "“Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "“That’s why, householder, you should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘na cakkhuṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me cakkhunissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the eye, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the eye.’"

msgctxt "mn143:5.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

msgctxt "mn143:5.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:5.5"
msgid "‘na sotaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me sotanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the ear, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the ear.’ …"

msgctxt "mn143:5.6"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.7"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.8"
msgid "‘na ghānaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me ghānanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the nose, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the nose.’ …"

msgctxt "mn143:5.9"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.10"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.11"
msgid "‘na jivhaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me jivhānissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the tongue, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the tongue.’ …"

msgctxt "mn143:5.12"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.13"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.14"
msgid "‘na kāyaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me kāyanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the body, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the body.’ …"

msgctxt "mn143:5.15"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.16"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:5.17"
msgid "‘na manaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me manonissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the mind, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the mind.’"

msgctxt "mn143:5.18"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (1)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:6.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:6.2"
msgid "‘na rūpaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me rūpanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp sights, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on sights.’ …"

msgctxt "mn143:6.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:6.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:6.5"
msgid "‘na saddaṃ upādiyissāmi … pe …"
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp sound …"

msgctxt "mn143:6.6"
msgid "na gandhaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "smell …"

msgctxt "mn143:6.7"
msgid "na rasaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "taste …"

msgctxt "mn143:6.8"
msgid "na phoṭṭhabbaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "touch …"

msgctxt "mn143:6.9"
msgid ""
"na dhammaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me dhammanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"thoughts, and there shall be no consciousness of mine dependent on thoughts.’"

msgctxt "mn143:6.10"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (2)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:7.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:7.2"
msgid ""
"‘na cakkhuviññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me cakkhuviññāṇanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp eye consciousness, and there shall be no consciousness of "
"mine dependent on eye consciousness.’ …"

msgctxt "mn143:7.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:7.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:7.5"
msgid "‘na sotaviññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp ear consciousness …"

msgctxt "mn143:7.6"
msgid "na ghānaviññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "nose consciousness …"

msgctxt "mn143:7.7"
msgid "na jivhāviññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "tongue consciousness …"

msgctxt "mn143:7.8"
msgid "na kāyaviññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "body consciousness …"

msgctxt "mn143:7.9"
msgid ""
"na manoviññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me manoviññāṇanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"mind consciousness, and there shall be no consciousness of mine dependent on "
"mind consciousness.’"

msgctxt "mn143:7.10"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (3)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.260"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:8.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:8.2"
msgid ""
"‘na cakkhusamphassaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me cakkhusamphassanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp eye contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:8.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:8.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:8.5"
msgid "‘na sotasamphassaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "ear contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:8.6"
msgid "na ghānasamphassaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "nose contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:8.7"
msgid "na jivhāsamphassaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "tongue contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:8.8"
msgid "na kāyasamphassaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "body contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:8.9"
msgid ""
"na manosamphassaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me manosamphassanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"mind contact, and there shall be no consciousness of mine dependent on mind "
"contact.’"

msgctxt "mn143:8.10"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (4)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:9.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:9.2"
msgid ""
"‘na cakkhusamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me "
"cakkhusamphassajāvedanānissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp feeling born of eye contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:9.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:9.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:9.5"
msgid "‘na sotasamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "feeling born of ear contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:9.6"
msgid "na ghānasamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "feeling born of nose contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:9.7"
msgid "na jivhāsamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "feeling born of tongue contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:9.8"
msgid "na kāyasamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "feeling born of body contact …"

msgctxt "mn143:9.9"
msgid ""
"na manosamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me "
"manosamphassajāvedanānissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"feeling born of mind contact, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on the feeling born of mind contact.’"

msgctxt "mn143:9.10"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (5)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:10.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘na pathavīdhātuṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me pathavīdhātunissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp the earth element …"

msgctxt "mn143:10.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:10.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:10.5"
msgid "‘na āpodhātuṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "water element …"

msgctxt "mn143:10.6"
msgid "na tejodhātuṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "fire element …"

msgctxt "mn143:10.7"
msgid "na vāyodhātuṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "air element …"

msgctxt "mn143:10.8"
msgid "na ākāsadhātuṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "space element …"

msgctxt "mn143:10.9"
msgid ""
"na viññāṇadhātuṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me viññāṇadhātunissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"consciousness element, and there shall be no consciousness of mine dependent "
"on the consciousness element.’"

msgctxt "mn143:10.10"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (6)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:11.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:11.2"
msgid "‘na rūpaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me rūpanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp form …"

msgctxt "mn143:11.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:11.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:11.5"
msgid "‘na vedanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "feeling …"

msgctxt "mn143:11.6"
msgid "na saññaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "mn143:11.7"
msgid "na saṅkhāre upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "mn143:11.8"
msgid ""
"na viññāṇaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me viññāṇanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"consciousness, and there shall be no consciousness of mine dependent on "
"consciousness.’"

msgctxt "mn143:11.9"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (7)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.261"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:12.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘na ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me ākāsānañcāyatananissitaṃ "
"viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr "‘I shall not grasp the dimension of infinite space …"

msgctxt "mn143:12.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:12.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:12.5"
msgid "‘na viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "the dimension of infinite consciousness …"

msgctxt "mn143:12.6"
msgid "na ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ upādiyissāmi …"
msgstr "the dimension of nothingness …"

msgctxt "mn143:12.7"
msgid ""
"na nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatananissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, and there shall be "
"no consciousness of mine dependent on the dimension of neither perception "
"nor non-perception.’"

msgctxt "mn143:12.8"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ. (8)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:13.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:13.2"
msgid ""
"‘na idhalokaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me idhalokanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp this world, and there shall be no consciousness of mine "
"dependent on this world.’"

msgctxt "mn143:13.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:14.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:14.2"
msgid ""
"‘na paralokaṃ upādiyissāmi, na ca me paralokanissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp the other world, and there shall be no consciousness of "
"mine dependent on the other world.’"

msgctxt "mn143:14.3"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

msgctxt "mn143:14.4"
msgid "Tasmātiha te, gahapati, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "You should train like this:"

msgctxt "mn143:14.5"
msgid ""
"‘yampi me diṭṭhaṃ sutaṃ mutaṃ viññātaṃ pattaṃ pariyesitaṃ anupariyesitaṃ "
"anucaritaṃ manasā tampi na upādiyissāmi, na ca me tannissitaṃ viññāṇaṃ "
"bhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I shall not grasp whatever is seen, heard, thought, cognized, searched, and "
"explored by my mind, and there shall be no consciousness of mine dependent "
"on that.’"

msgctxt "mn143:14.6"
msgid "Evañhi te, gahapati, sikkhitabban”ti. (9)"
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:15.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati parodi, assūni pavattesi."
msgstr "When he said this, Anāthapiṇḍika cried and burst out in tears."

msgctxt "mn143:15.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Venerable Ānanda said to him:"

msgctxt "mn143:15.3"
msgid "“olīyasi kho tvaṃ, gahapati, saṃsīdasi kho tvaṃ, gahapatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Are you failing, householder? Are you fading, householder?”"

msgctxt "mn143:15.4"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bhante ānanda, olīyāmi, napi saṃsīdāmi;"
msgstr "“No, sir."

msgctxt "mn143:15.5"
msgid "api ca me dīgharattaṃ satthā payirupāsito manobhāvanīyā ca bhikkhū;"
msgstr ""
"But for a long time I have paid homage to the Buddha and the esteemed "
"mendicants."

msgctxt "mn143:15.6"
msgid "na ca me evarūpī dhammī kathā sutapubbā”ti."
msgstr "Yet I have never before heard such a Dhamma talk.”"

# Note that the verb here is patibhati. Rather than saying such talk is never given to lay people, patibhati refers to the spontaneous occurrence of the urge to give a Dhamma talk on such and such a topic.
msgctxt "mn143:15.7"
msgid ""
"“Na kho, gahapati, gihīnaṃ odātavasanānaṃ evarūpī dhammī kathā paṭibhāti;"
msgstr ""
"“Householder, it does not occur to us to teach such Dhamma talk to white-"
"clothed laypeople."

msgctxt "mn143:15.8"
msgid "pabbajitānaṃ kho, gahapati, evarūpī dhammī kathā paṭibhātī”ti."
msgstr "Rather, we teach like this to those gone forth.”"

msgctxt "mn143:15.9"
msgid ""
"“Tena hi, bhante sāriputta, gihīnampi odātavasanānaṃ evarūpī dhammī kathā "
"paṭibhātu."
msgstr ""
"“Well then, Master Sāriputta, let it occur to you to teach such Dhamma talk "
"to white-clothed laypeople as well!"

msgctxt "mn143:15.10"
msgid ""
"Santi hi, bhante, kulaputtā apparajakkhajātikā, assavanatā dhammassa "
"parihāyanti;"
msgstr ""
"There are members of good families with little dust in their eyes. They’re "
"in decline because they haven’t heard the teaching."

msgctxt "mn143:15.11"
msgid "bhavissanti dhammassa aññātāro”ti."
msgstr "There will be those who understand the teaching!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.262"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:16.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ca sāriputto āyasmā ca ānando anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ iminā "
"ovādena ovaditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"And when Venerables Sāriputta and Ānanda had given the householder "
"Anāthapiṇḍika this advice they got up from their seat and left."

msgctxt "mn143:16.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati, acirapakkante āyasmante ca sāriputte "
"āyasmante ca ānande, kālamakāsi tusitaṃ kāyaṃ upapajji."
msgstr ""
"Not long after they had left, Anāthapiṇḍika passed away and was reborn in "
"the group of Joyful Gods."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:17.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo "
"kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, the glorious god Anāthapiṇḍika, lighting up the entire "
"Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side,"

msgctxt "mn143:17.2"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhagavantaṃ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "and addressed the Buddha in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:17.3"
msgid "“Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ,"
msgstr "“This is indeed that Jeta’s Grove,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.4"
msgid "isisaṅghanisevitaṃ;"
msgstr "frequented by the Saṅgha of hermits,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.5"
msgid "Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena,"
msgstr "where the King of Dhamma stayed:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.6"
msgid "pītisañjananaṃ mama."
msgstr "it brings me joy!"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:17.7"
msgid "Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca,"
msgstr "Deeds, knowledge, and principle;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.8"
msgid "sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ;"
msgstr "ethical conduct, an excellent livelihood;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.9"
msgid "Etena maccā sujjhanti,"
msgstr "by these are mortals purified,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.10"
msgid "na gottena dhanena vā."
msgstr "not by clan or wealth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:17.11"
msgid "Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso,"
msgstr "That’s why an astute person,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.12"
msgid "sampassaṃ atthamattano;"
msgstr "seeing what’s good for themselves,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.13"
msgid "Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ,"
msgstr "would examine the teaching rationally,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.14"
msgid "evaṃ tattha visujjhati."
msgstr "and thus be purified in it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:17.15"
msgid "Sāriputtova paññāya,"
msgstr "Sāriputta has true wisdom,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.16"
msgid "sīlena upasamena ca;"
msgstr "ethics, and also peace."

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.17"
msgid "Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu,"
msgstr "Any mendicant who has crossed over"

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:17.18"
msgid "etāvaparamo siyā”ti."
msgstr "can at best equal him.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:18.1"
msgid "Idamavoca anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto."
msgstr "This is what the god Anāthapiṇḍika said,"

msgctxt "mn143:18.2"
msgid "Samanuñño satthā ahosi."
msgstr "and the teacher approved."

msgctxt "mn143:18.3"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto:"
msgstr "Then the god Anāthapiṇḍika,"

msgctxt "mn143:18.4"
msgid ""
"“samanuñño me satthā”ti bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā "
"tatthevantaradhāyi."
msgstr ""
"knowing that the teacher approved, bowed and respectfully circled the "
"Buddha, keeping him on his right, before vanishing right there."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:19.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha told the mendicants all that had "
"happened."

msgctxt "mn143:19.2"
msgid ""
"“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññataro devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:19.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho so devaputto maṃ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:19.4"
msgid "‘Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.5"
msgid "isisaṅghanisevitaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.6"
msgid "Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.7"
msgid "pītisañjananaṃ mama."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:19.8"
msgid "Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.9"
msgid "sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.10"
msgid "Etena maccā sujjhanti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.11"
msgid "na gottena dhanena vā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:19.12"
msgid "Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.13"
msgid "sampassaṃ atthamattano;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.14"
msgid "Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.15"
msgid "evaṃ tattha visujjhati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:19.16"
msgid "Sāriputtova paññāya,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.17"
msgid "sīlena upasamena ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.18"
msgid "Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn143:19.19"
msgid "etāvaparamo siyā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.263"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:19.20"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, so devaputto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn143:19.21"
msgid ""
"‘Samanuñño me satthā’ti maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā "
"tatthevantaradhāyī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:20.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, Venerable Ānanda said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "mn143:20.2"
msgid "“so hi nūna so, bhante, anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhavissati."
msgstr "“Sir, that god must surely have been Anāthapiṇḍika."

msgctxt "mn143:20.3"
msgid ""
"Anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati āyasmante sāriputte abhippasanno ahosī”ti."
msgstr "For the householder Anāthapiṇḍika was devoted to Venerable Sāriputta.”"

msgctxt "mn143:20.4"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, ānanda."
msgstr "“Good, good, Ānanda."

msgctxt "mn143:20.5"
msgid "Yāvatakaṃ kho, ānanda, takkāya pattabbaṃ, anuppattaṃ taṃ tayā."
msgstr "You’ve reached the logical conclusion, as far as logic goes."

msgctxt "mn143:20.6"
msgid "Anāthapiṇḍiko so, ānanda, devaputto”ti."
msgstr "For that was indeed the god Anāthapiṇḍika.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "mn143:20.7"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn143:20.8"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā ānando bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Ānanda was happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn143:20.9"
msgid "Anāthapiṇḍikovādasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
